@DATABASE "Ricochet"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - R - Ricochet"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - R
                   ====================================

                                 Ricochet
                                 ========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37398,0)"}          37398,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(32866,255)"}          32866,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
